CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 23, 1945, pg. 18, reads: " Nuptials Announced - Miss Beulah Smith, daughter of Mr. and Mrs. William Smith, and Earl Henderson, son of Mrs. Rosalee Collins, were married Sunday, June 10, at the Trinity AME Church. A reception for the newlyweds was given at the home of the groom's mother, 402 Robinson Court. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Groom Earl Henderson and bride Beulah Smith Henderson posed in Harris Studio
